in the AFC archive.

00:04:18.380 --> 00:04:23.110
And it's entitled Alan
Lomax and Haiti, 1936 to 37.

00:04:23.110 --> 00:04:27.160
And it was named as an
outstanding project in 2010

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:31.640 position:56%
by the Clinton Global Initiative
and received two Grammy nominations.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:35.780 position:56%
In addition to his Haitian research,
