musicology, Trinidadian steel bands,

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:45.970
music of the African Diaspora,
world music ensembles,

00:04:45.970 --> 00:04:51.940
Alan Lomax's Choreometrics
Projects and music and militarism.

00:04:51.940 --> 00:04:56.270
We are delighted to have him
with us today, coming all the way

00:04:56.270 --> 00:04:58.310
