Spanish, the National Library.

00:08:18.070 --> 00:08:23.140
And so, and of course, many of
the most important collections

00:08:23.140 --> 00:08:25.310
in Haiti are private collections.

00:08:25.310 --> 00:08:28.710
They're in people's homes where
they're exposed to the elements.

00:08:28.710 --> 00:08:33.680
They're exposed to, of course,
the death of the owners, theft,

00:08:33.680 --> 00:08:35.910
natural disasters, etcetera.

00:08:35.910 --> 00:08:42.460
And so it's against this background
of precarious cultural reserves

00:08:42.460 --> 00:08:45.370
