societies in the region.

00:56:08.010 --> 00:56:10.420
And it was really quite amazing,
some of the old [inaudible],

00:56:10.420 --> 00:56:14.800
the [foreign language] in
the audience are nodding.

00:56:14.800 --> 00:56:17.280
And you can see the
words starting to form.

00:56:17.280 --> 00:56:20.260
And many of these songs
people hadn't heard in,

00:56:20.260 --> 00:56:22.590
you know, 50, 60 years.

00:56:22.590 --> 00:56:27.020
And the ceremony captured that.

00:56:27.020 --> 00:56:29.940
I went out to speak with a very
well-known oongar [phonetic]

00:56:29.940 --> 00:56:34.040
