00:57:53.600 --> 00:57:58.040
And they took the stage to tent
cities, to [foreign language],

00:57:58.040 --> 00:58:03.620
the most difficult
places to live in Haiti.

00:58:03.620 --> 00:58:11.230
And then we took it
altogether again out to Leogane

00:58:11.230 --> 00:58:13.610
to show cultural materials.

00:58:13.610 --> 00:58:14.910
There was music.

00:58:14.910 --> 00:58:17.910
But then the Lomax
materials were included.

00:58:17.910 --> 00:58:20.200
And the night of the
concert in the cow field

00:58:20.200 --> 00:58:21.910
