00:59:01.150 --> 00:59:02.450
[Foreign language].

00:59:02.450 --> 00:59:03.750
And people started applauded.

00:59:03.750 --> 00:59:06.450
And I'm emphasizing these
moments because they meant a lot

00:59:06.450 --> 00:59:08.510
