who we're up against.

00:59:42.450 --> 00:59:44.420
She said who?

00:59:44.420 --> 00:59:45.720
Sleepy head.

00:59:45.720 --> 00:59:47.020
I said, the Beetles.

00:59:47.020 --> 00:59:49.810
And she said, my Beetles?

00:59:49.810 --> 00:59:52.210
And I said, yeah, your Beetles.

00:59:52.210 --> 00:59:56.400
And I said their box set is our
principal competitor for, you know.

00:59:56.400 --> 00:59:58.730
